3013
3014static int
3015lookup_handler (unsigned scode)
3016{
3017 int l = 0, h = ARRAY_SIZE (pats), m;
3018 while (h > l)
3019 {
3020 m = (h + l) / 2;
3021 if (scode == pats[m].scode)
3022 return m;
3023 else if (scode < pats[m].scode)
3024 h = m;
3025 else
3026 l = m + 1;
3027 }
3028 return -1;
3029}
3030
3031enum insn_code
3032raw_optab_handler (unsigned scode)
3033{
3034 int i = lookup_handler (scode);
3035 return (i >= 0 && this_fn_optabs->pat_enable[i]
3036 ? pats[i].icode : CODE_FOR_nothing);
3037}
3038
3039bool
3040swap_optab_enable (optab op, machine_mode m, bool set)
3041{
3042 unsigned scode = (op << 16) | m;
3043 int i = lookup_handler (scode);
3044 if (i >= 0)
3045 {
3046 bool ret = this_fn_optabs->pat_enable[i];
3047 this_fn_optabs->pat_enable[i] = set;
3048 return ret;
3049 }
3050 else
3051 {
3052 gcc_assert (!set);
3053 return false;
3054 }
3055}
